{"data":[{"date":"11:16 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-dortmund-03h00-ngay-237-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool vs Dortmund l\u00fac 03h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 237 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 237 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2272018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool vs Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Liverpool vs Dortmund: 3-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa TTCN m\u00f9a H\u00e8 m\u1edbi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. R\u1ea5t nhanh, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Fabinho, Shaqiri hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ngay t\u1eeb n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u00ec Liverpool c\u0169ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 xong ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Naby Keita. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0, t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y The Kop \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u 3 tuy\u1ebfn. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Juergen Klopp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Liverpool shopping r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh tay \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 m\u00f9a H\u00e8 c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. M\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. \u1ede Premier League th\u00ec The Kop lu\u00f4n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4. N\u0103m nay, Klopp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi d\u00e0n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah, Roberto Firmino, Sadio Mane, Van Dijk, Jordan Henderson\u2026, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd Premier League 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u The Kop \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t trong Big Six. Ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a H\u00e8. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0 1/4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t, Blackburn. Vi\u1ec7c 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Daniel Sturridge v\u00e0 Lazar Markovic ghi b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Liverpool c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Blackburn. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00eam nay th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1edbn, Liverpool nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi Dortmund. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111ang trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Lucien Favre. C\u1ef1u HLV Nice c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Klopp coi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 khung r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u00ec Favre l\u1ea1i coi giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u khi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t Liverpool nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, Juergen Klopp s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Dortmund. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Liverpool th\u00ec Klopp t\u1eebng c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Dortmund. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Dortmund hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Klopp, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Mario Goetze. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Dortmund tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Liverpool. Hai l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out Europa League 2015/16. Klopp gi\u00e0nh 1 tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Juergen Klopp (Liverpool): \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Liverpool ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lucien Favre (Dortmund): \u201cLiverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u00edch lu\u1ef9 th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- Liverpool th\u1eafng 8, thua 11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n- 13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\n- Dortmund th\u1eafng 9, thua 11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n- 9/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1: 15/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung hi\u1ec7p 1. 14/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. NHM n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i sau 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4479","checkdouble":"191776"},{"date":"09:16 22/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Napoli","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-hlv-chelsea-bi-chi-trich-te-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-napoli.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o c\u1ef1u HLV Maurizio Sarri ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Napoli sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Napoli \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 \u201cc\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1p\u201d cho Chelsea nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u1eeb HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Jorginho. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chu-tich-Napoli-chi-trich-HLV-Sarri-phu-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, Sarri v\u00e0 Napoli v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n chia tay trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb s\u1ebfp c\u0169 l\u00ean \u00e1n s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c, vong \u01a1n b\u1ed9i ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cH\u1eafn ta n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u1eafn ta v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef im l\u1eb7ng. Gi\u1edd h\u1eafn ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f2n r\u00fat ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tham lam nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u1eafn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u01b0\u1edbp c\u1ea3 Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. H\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n Jorginho th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u00e2n HLV Carlo Ancelotti n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o Amadou Diawara ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00e9o Marek Hamsik xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</span><br>\r\nGianfranco Zola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tay ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4478","checkdouble":"191768"},{"date":"10:28 22/07","title":"Klopp: \"MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mua s\u1eafm b\u1ea1t m\u1ea1ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn Liverpool tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u, ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o Man Utd c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m, c\u01a1 m\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016 khi Man Utd ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00ec Paul Pogba, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f5ng d\u1ea1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u00ec Liverpool b\u1ea1o chi nh\u01b0 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u00ec Liverpool b\u1ea1o chi nh\u01b0 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 cho 4 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Klopp gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u, ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o Man Utd nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng d\u1ea1i g\u00ec gi\u1eef \u0111\u00fang l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a m\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng quan t\u00e2m th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y ngh\u0129 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c Man Utd ch\u1eb3ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 mang t\u00ednh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng sai, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u00f2n h\u01a1n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o. Th\u1eddi th\u1ebf thay \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ti\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u1eady th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng n\u00f3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed5i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i thay \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Pogba m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai-172-191662.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai-172-191662.html\">Liverpool bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai?</span><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn xu\u00f4i theo d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y c\u1ee7a Premier League m\u00e0 Alisson Becker l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t cho s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n d\u1ecbch trong t\u01b0 duy c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4477","checkdouble":"191769"},{"date":"09:15 22/07","title":"Mahrez h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/mahrez-hai-long-voi-man-ra-mat-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez vui m\u1eebng khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Man City d\u00f9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-1.</h2><h2>Mahrez ra m\u1eaft Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Riyad Mahrez c\u00f3 72 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/man-city-vs-dortmund-icc-2018-372-191691.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man City t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9</span>. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Dortmund l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mario Gotze \u1edf ph\u00fat 28.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahrez c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Marwin Hitz. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mahrez h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/mahrez-hai-long-voi-man-ra-mat-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mahrez ra m\u1eaft Man City trong tr\u1eadn thua Dortmund</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Mahrez h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i ICC</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Man xanh s\u1ebd bay \u0111\u1ebfn New York v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1eb7p Liverpool t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n MetLife.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi trong 2 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. V\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ea1i Emirates v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12/8. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leicester tin r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3. Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 Arsenal m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft n\u1eefa. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong 3 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1edbi n\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phan-tich-cac-sao-mai-man-city-trong-tran-thua-dortmund-172-191742.html\">Guardiola ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c sao mai Man City trong tr\u1eadn thua Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-hai-long-voi-mahrez-172-191733.html\">Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Guardiola v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4476","checkdouble":"191771"},{"date":"11:20 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh San Jose Earthquakes vs MU 04h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/nhan-dinh-san-jose-earthquakes-vs-mu-04h00-ngay-237-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>San Jose Earthquakes vs MU l\u00fac 04h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh San Jose Earthquakes vs MU 04h00 ng\u00e0y 237 Giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh San Jose Earthquakes vs MU 04h00 ng\u00e0y 237 Giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/San-Jose-Earthquakes-vs-Man-United.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">San Jose Earthquakes vs MU</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>San Jose Earthquakes vs MU: 0-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1eafc M\u1ef9, Man United t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i San Jose 3-1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Depay, Mata v\u00e0 Pereira. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Nh\u01b0ng hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Man United v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd\u2026 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose \u0111\u00eam nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Levi\u2019s Stadium, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a San Jose v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u00e0n sao Man United. \u0110\u00e3 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ebfn hai \u201ctay s\u00fang\u201d t\u1eebng b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 San Jose c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, trong \u0111\u00f3 Mata \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao khi anh v\u1eeba ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Club America 1-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 San Jose c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0n sao Man United. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mong ch\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng n\u01a1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed b\u1ed9 ba Martial \u2013 Mitchell \u2013 Mata n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Club America. Hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Mata nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chu\u1ed9c l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Anthony Martial v\u00e0 Demetri Mitchell, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial t\u1eebng c\u00f4ng khai \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Man United cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2017/18 nh\u01b0ng Mourinho \u0111ang trao cho anh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng. C\u00f2n Mitchell l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y t\u1eebng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Crystal Palace \u1edf Premier League cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00eam nay, anh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Club America n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Herrera s\u1ebd g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Man United trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Pogba, Lingard c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup. Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Club America, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Mata d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jiminez c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Mexico k\u1ecbp c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. \u0110\u00eam nay, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, h\u1eb3n Mata v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- San Jose \u0111\u00e3 thua theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 4 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n- 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng<br>\r\n- 4 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a San Jose k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ch\u1eb5n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: 8 tr\u00ean 10 hi\u1ec7p 1 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a San Jose \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 10 hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u00f3. Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 6/10 hi\u1ec7p 1 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4475","checkdouble":"191777"},{"date":"07:19 22/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 22/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2207 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2207 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-MU-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nIvan Perisic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV c\u1ee7a Inter, Luciano Spalletti.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Giroud</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Italia, Gianluca Di Marzio Atletico Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ander Herrera mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2019, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Welbeck v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\">V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</span><br>\r\nDanny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Magui l\u00ean 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Digne&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca ban Digne cho Juventus o He 2018\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Digne cho Juventus \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Barca-ban-Lucas-Digne-cho-Everton-voi-gia-16-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Digne s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Everton ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Bayern Munich c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Karim Benzema s\u1eafp t\u1edbi AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sport, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4474","checkdouble":"191766"},{"date":"07:12 22/07","title":"S\u1ed1c: Arsenal l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer c\u1ee7a Monchengladbach, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cech v\u00e0 Ospina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Bernd Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea3 David Ospina v\u00e0 Petr Cech l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, c\u1ea3 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Arsenal-muon-mua-Yann-Sommer-thay-Petr-Cech-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech v\u00e0 Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDavid Ospina \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 quan t\u00e2m, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Ph\u00eda Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPetr Cech hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m. The Blues \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t Courtois v\u00e0o tay Real Madrid, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1982 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Napoli c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Cech.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 David Ospina v\u00e0 Petr Cech \u0111\u1ec1u ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Arsenal bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Bernd Leno.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yann Sommer</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer c\u1ee7a Monchengladbach, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nYann Sommer \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Bundesliga cho CLB Monchengladbach, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yann Sommer \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Monchengladbach sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Monchengladbach y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Leno, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4473","checkdouble":"191764"},{"date":"08:35 22/07","title":"Pereira: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andreas Pereira quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man United m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Valencia theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</h2><h2>Pereira quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pereira \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Mestalla trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-that-vong-voi-quyet-dinh-ra-di-cua-pereira-172-167901.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Pereira</span> v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. V\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ho\u00e0i nghi r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Pereira cho r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf Valencia v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cQu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Man United. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Michael Carrick, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau 12 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cHLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 6. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. HLV lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i cho t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCarrick c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 h\u1ecd m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCarrick l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0a ra cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o nh\u1ecf, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u00f4i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. B\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 nhanh v\u00e0 th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-anh-len-65-trieu-bang-172-191763.html\">MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4472","checkdouble":"191767"},{"date":"08:54 22/07","title":"M\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, Herrera v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 \u1edf MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/mat-vi-tri-herrera-van-quyet-tam-bam-tru-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.</h2><h2>Herrera mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 12 th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 5 c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-cong-bo-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-khong-phai-ibrahimovic-172-160221.html\" target=\"_blank\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t MU m\u00f9a 2016/17</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 161 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/mat-vi-tri-herrera-van-quyet-tam-bam-tru-o-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHerrera hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Man United nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa d\u00f9 \u0111ang v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi San Jose Earthquakes, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 chia s\u1ebb:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. V\u1eady n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i y\u00eau n\u01a1i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU n\u0103m t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Herrera \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man United gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup, League Cup v\u00e0 Europa League trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Anh. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong n\u0103m m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch hay West Brom tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eadt s\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng thi tho\u1ea3ng v\u1eabn m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu-172-191767.html\">Pereira: T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia-184-191766.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4471","checkdouble":"191770"},{"date":"21:15 21/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-hagl-tren-san-vinh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn.</h2><h2>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea1i Vinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/HLV-Duong-Minh-Ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-HAGL-tren-san-Vinh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng CLB HAGL kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00ec y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/7, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p CLB SLNA. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 SLNA khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-1 chung cu\u1ed9c nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Chi\u1ec1u nay, tr\u1eddi ch\u01b0a m\u01b0a l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 c\u01a1n m\u01b0a nh\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thua. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u00e2ng cao khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua th\u00eam b\u00e0n n\u1eefa\", HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi hai ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a SLNA l\u00e0 Olaha v\u00e0 Lynch Jermine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olaha t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t khi ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au g\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, song \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191726.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191726.html\">SLNA 3-1 HAGL (KT): \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf V-League 2018</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 8, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m tranh ch\u1ea5p huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4470","checkdouble":"191750"},{"date":"21:32 21/07","title":"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/ha-dep-hagl-slna-bat-kip-ky-luc-vleague-13-nam-truoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eeba b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 13 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL.</h2><h2>SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League sau 13 n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB SLNA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i \u2018ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda\u2019 Vinh \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/6_Zing_3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Olaha sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa SLNA \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 b\u00e0n nh\u1edd pha ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n\u00a0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap SLNA gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd san b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 13 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u1ea1i V-League 2005.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, SLNA s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1edfi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 21, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao v\u1eabn c\u00f2n g\u1ea7n hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 SLNA chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Sau v\u00f2ng 20 n\u00e0y, V-League 2018 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 21 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 8/9 t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4469","checkdouble":"191752"},{"date":"06:30 22/07","title":"Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/thua-nguoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-phai-thua-nhan-mot-su-that.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><h2>HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 tinh qu\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/video-tong-hop-thanh-hoa-23-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0FLC Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/7, ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Thanh H\u00f3a b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Chung ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 64 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eafng. Ba b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 42 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hai, trong khi CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay 51 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i sau 1, 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p nh\u1eadn huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4468","checkdouble":"191753"},{"date":"22:32 21/07","title":"Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/lien-tiep-toa-sang-tien-linh-van-chua-nghi-toi-cuoc-chay-dua-voi-tien-linh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-Leauge</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/7, t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so g\u0103ng gi\u1eefa hai ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1997 v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ASIAD. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u nay, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 11. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3 b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, d\u00f9 \u2018t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u2019 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n mang theo tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4467","checkdouble":"191754"}]}